07ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">0</span></span></a> - Lua plugin to parse Youtube playlists.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Trevelopment/vlc-super-skipper\">vlc-super-skipper</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Trevelopment/vlc-super-skipper\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">6</span></span></a> - Automatically Skip Opening and Ending Sequences.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"apps\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#apps\" aria-label=\"apps permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Apps</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://code.videolan.org/videolan/vlc\">VLC desktop</a> - The original Desktop app running on Linux/Windows (Qt) and macOS (Cocoa).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://code.videolan.org/videolan/vlc-ios\">VLC iOS</a> - VLC for iOS is the official port of VLC on the iOS/tvOS platforms.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://code.videolan.org/videolan/vlc-android\">VLC Android</a> - VLC for Android, Android TV and ChromeOS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://code.videolan.org/videolan/vlc-bench\">VLC Benchmark (Beta)</a> - Video decoding and rendering benchmark tool, based on VLC.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"bindings\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bindings\" aria-label=\"bindings permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Bindings</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://code.videolan.org/videolan/VLCKit\">VLCKit</a> - The libvlc bindings for macOS, iOS, iPadOS and tvOS in Objective-C.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://code.videolan.org/videolan/vlc-android/-/tree/master/libvlc\">libvlcjni</a> - The libvlc bindings for the Android platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://code.videolan.org/videolan/vlc-unity\">vlc-unity</a> - Unity3D integration for VLC.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oaubert/python-vlc\">python-vlc</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/oaubert/python-vlc\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">296</span></span></a> - Python vlc bindings.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/caprica/vlcj\">vlcj</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/caprica/vlcj\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative